'''''Parma Nölé'' 13-14''' is the thirteenth/fourteenth issue produced by the [[North East Tolkien Society]] ''[[Parma Nölé]]'', released Summer 2005 as a double issue.

==Contents==
* Letter from the Editor
* Melissa S. Gibson: "Language & Literature, The Courtship of Valinor and Iceland"
* [[Mark T. Hooker]]: "Frodo Quartermain"
* [[Deborah Singer]]: "An Interview with the band [[Hobbit (band)|Hobbit]]"
* [[Deborah Singer]]: "Memories of Marquette"
* Namiko Hitosubashi: "Lady of Rohan"
* Kristyna Lavicka: "How to Go On"
* Aravis: "Discovering Rammoth"
